              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                QUESTION<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Whether societies of men are really capable or not，of establishing good government from reflection and choice，or whether they are forever destined to depend，for their political constitutions，on accident and force?<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Reflection and Choice   OR   Accident and Force  ？
